Last month a woman who tortured her teenage brother to death after accusing him of witchcraft was jailed for life.

Magalie Bamu and her boyfriend Eric Bikubi inflicted more than 130 injuries on 15-year-old Kristy Bamu over the course of a horrific four-day attack in Newham, east London.

